---
title: Dilly Cheddar Scone Sandos with Bacon plus Roasted Veggie Filling, Quickles & Dijonnaise
description: Ready for a great weekend project? How do you feel about using scones as sandwich bread? Excellent, you say? Great! You’ll make flaky homemade cheddar-dill scones, slice ‘em up, spread with tangy-creamy Dijonnaise, and fill with roasted carrots and onion, plus quick cucumber pickles for tangy freshness. Get ready for from-scratch cooking at its finest.

